---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import QuickSummary from '../components/QuickSummary.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Alliance Tools" 
  description="Ready-to-copy daily VS focus messages, Alliance Trial posts, and Monica elite rally reminders for Last War: Survival alliance leaders."
>
  <h1>Alliance Tools</h1>
  <p class="text-lg text-[#8a96b0]">Copy, paste, win. Replace anything in [brackets] with your actual numbers.</p>

  <QuickSummary>
    <p>Consistent, clear alliance communication is one of the highest-ROI things a leader can do. These templates are battle-tested patterns used by strong mid-game alliances.</p>
  </QuickSummary>

  <h2>Daily VS Focus</h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-[#8a96b0]">Post one of these (or a variation) in alliance chat every day during VS.</p>

  <div class="card p-4 mb-4">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
      <div class="font-semibold">General VS Focus Message</div>
      <button class="copy-btn text-xs" data-copy="Today’s VS focus: Prioritize [Day-specific goal, e.g. Hero Shards / Gear / Research]. We need strong participation in the 8pm rally window. Let’s push for top 3 on server!">Copy</button>
    </div>
    <pre class="text-sm bg-[#0b1220] p-3 rounded overflow-x-auto text-[#c4b5fd]">Today’s VS focus: Prioritize [Hero Shards / Gear Materials / Research Speed]. 

We’re aiming for strong participation in the evening rally window. Every point helps the alliance.

Let’s finish in the top 3 on server today!</pre>
  </div>

  <h2>Alliance Trial / 2x Events</h2>
  <div class="card p-4 mb-4">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
      <div class="font-semibold">Alliance Trial Reminder</div>
      <button class="copy-btn text-xs" data-copy="Alliance Trial starts in ~30 min. Bring your best squad and be ready to rally. Focus on [specific boss or stage] for max points. Let’s clear it fast!">Copy</button>
    </div>
    <pre class="text-sm bg-[#0b1220] p-3 rounded overflow-x-auto">Alliance Trial starts in ~30 min. 

Bring your best squad and be ready to rally on the main target. 

Focus fire and we’ll clear it quickly. Good luck everyone!</pre>
  </div>

  <h2>Monica Elite Rally Call</h2>
  <div class="card p-4 mb-6">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
      <div class="font-semibold">Doomed Elite Farming (with Monica)</div>
      <button class="copy-btn text-xs" data-copy="Reminder: For Doomed Elite rallies, please try to include Monica in your squad (even at low stars). Her skill gives a big resource bonus on elites. Swap her in for farming runs — it adds up fast for the whole alliance.">Copy</button>
    </div>
    <pre class="text-sm bg-[#0b1220] p-3 rounded overflow-x-auto">Reminder for elite farming: 

Include Monica in your squad when hitting Doomed Elites (lead or join). Her resource bonus is significant and helps everyone.

You can swap her back out for combat content afterward. Small effort, big RSS gains.</pre>
  </div>

  <h2>Other High-ROI Templates</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-4">
    <div class="card p-4">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
        <div class="font-semibold text-sm">Wall of Honor / Shard Push</div>
        <button class="copy-btn text-xs" data-copy="Wall of Honor push this week for [Hero Name]. If you have shards for them, please use them this week. Every star helps the whole alliance in events.">Copy</button>
      </div>
      <pre class="text-xs bg-[#0b1220] p-2 rounded">Wall of Honor push this week for [Hero Name]. If you have shards for them, please use them this week. Every star helps the whole alliance in events.</pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-4">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
        <div class="font-semibold text-sm">Arms Race Coordination</div>
        <button class="copy-btn text-xs" data-copy="Arms Race reminder: Save your big stamina and legendary chests for the final 3-4 hours. We will pop together for max alliance gifts. Smaller chests are fine to open earlier for dailies.">Copy</button>
      </div>
      <pre class="text-xs bg-[#0b1220] p-2 rounded">Arms Race reminder: Save your big stamina and legendary chests for the final 3-4 hours. We will pop together for max alliance gifts. Smaller chests are fine to open earlier for dailies.</pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-4">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
        <div class="font-semibold text-sm">New Member Onboarding</div>
        <button class="copy-btn text-xs" data-copy="Welcome! Please read the pinned Squad Building guide before asking hero questions. We strongly follow 'Main Squad First' — almost all resources go into one squad until it's very strong.">Copy</button>
      </div>
      <pre class="text-xs bg-[#0b1220] p-2 rounded">Welcome! Please read the pinned Squad Building guide before asking hero questions. We strongly follow 'Main Squad First' — almost all resources go into one squad until it's very strong.</pre>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-4">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
        <div class="font-semibold text-sm">VS Participation Push</div>
        <button class="copy-btn text-xs" data-copy="VS is live. Please participate in the evening rally window if possible. Every point moves us up the server rankings and improves our rewards. Let’s go!">Copy</button>
      </div>
      <pre class="text-xs bg-[#0b1220] p-2 rounded">VS is live. Please participate in the evening rally window if possible. Every point moves us up the server rankings and improves our rewards. Let’s go!</pre>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    // Vanilla copy-to-clipboard for alliance messages (no React needed)
    document.querySelectorAll('.copy-btn').forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', async () => {
        const text = btn.getAttribute('data-copy');
        if (!text) return;

        try {
          await navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);
          const originalText = btn.textContent;
          btn.textContent = 'Copied!';
          btn.classList.add('copied');

          setTimeout(() => {
            btn.textContent = originalText;
            btn.classList.remove('copied');
          }, 1800);
        } catch (err) {
          // Fallback for older browsers
          const textarea = document.createElement('textarea');
          textarea.value = text;
          document.body.appendChild(textarea);
          textarea.select();
          document.execCommand('copy');
          document.body.removeChild(textarea);
          btn.textContent = 'Copied!';
          setTimeout(() => { btn.textContent = 'Copy'; }, 1800);
        }
      });
    });
  </script>
</Layout>